summary: He's a chicken (or at least he thinks he is) in the form of a man.
descriptionHtml:
[size=3][img]http://i.imgur.com/KOW1Rt3.jpg[/img]
Chickenman is a chicken (or at least he thinks he is) in the form of a man. Nobody knows where he comes from, and nobody questions him. He spends his days on Battle-Born Farm praying and performing rituals for his great cousins. Approach him and he may join your adventure. 

Being the most high quality mod of the century, this mod offers: 

-A Chickenman 
-???? 
-A Chickenman 

Chickenman comes with his very own Ritual Dagger and Conjure Chicken Spell.[/size]
author: Ghille
